Package: TimeSeriesR
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Time Series Data Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2024-12-20
Author: Alexander Klaus, Clemens Glomb, Daniela Staengle, Philip Kastura-Sahl, Sebastian Meier
Maintainer: Alexander Klaus
Description: This package provides tools for the analysis of time series data, with a focus on autoregressive (AR) and moving average (MA) processes. It supports the simulation of these processes and the estimation of their properties, enabling both exploratory and confirmatory analysis of time series data.
